<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>JUANJE | Ingeniería de Conversión 360°</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['"Plus Jakarta Sans"', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['"Playfair Display"', 'serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .subtle-grid {
            background-image: radial-gradient(#e2e8f0 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 32px 32px;
        }
        .luxury-shadow {
            box-shadow: 0 32px 64px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .text-balance {
            text-wrap: balance;
        }
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-[#0f172a] font-sans selection:bg-[#0f172a] selection:text-white overflow-x-hidden">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-100">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#0f172a] flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">
                <i data-lucide="layers" class="w-4 h-4 text-white"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="font-bold tracking-tighter text-xl">JUANJE.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 items-center">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Estrategia 360°</span>
            <a href="#audit-section" class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#0f172a] text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all">
                Solicitar Auditoría
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-20 px-8 lg:px-20 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center subtle-grid">
        <div class="max-w-5xl space-y-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-100 rounded-full mb-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-600">Análisis de Mercado en Tiempo Real</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="font-sans text-5xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-balance uppercase">
                DEJA QUE LOS CLIENTES <br />
                <span class="text-blue-600 italic font-serif normal-case">se acerquen a ti.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
                No es marketing. Es <span class="text-[#0f172a] font-bold underline decoration-blue-500 decoration-4">Ingeniería de Conversión</span>. Integramos SEO, SEM y Redes Sociales en un solo sistema de análisis 360° diseñado para capturar el deseo de tu cliente.
            </p>

            <div class="pt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
                <a href="#audit-section" class="px-12 py-6 bg-[#0f172a] text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm rounded-full luxury-shadow transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Iniciar Auditoría de Negocio
                </a>
                
                <div class="flex gap-12 text-slate-400 font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600"></i>
                        <span>SEO Local</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600"></i>
                        <span>SEM ROI+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600"></i>
                        <span>Social Neuro</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy -->
    <section class="py-32 px-8 lg:px-20 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <h2 class="font-sans text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none">
                        VENDER ES UN <br />
                        <span class="text-blue-600 italic font-serif">PROCESO MENTAL.</span>
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        <p>
                            Siguiendo los principios de <span class="text-[#0f172a] font-bold">Joseph Sugarman</span>, creamos un "tobogán" de ventas donde el cliente no puede evitar deslizarse hasta la conversión.
                        </p>
                        <p class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 italic text-slate-500">
                            "El deseo no se crea. Se canaliza." — Eugene Schwartz.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Nuestro sistema 360° no intenta convencer. Analiza dónde está el deseo de tu mercado y posiciona tu negocio como la única solución lógica.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">
                            <i data-lucide="search" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0f172a] group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">SEO de Captura</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">No buscamos tráfico, buscamos intención de compra.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">
                            <i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0f172a] group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">SEM de Precisión</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Anuncios que activan disparadores psicológicos.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">
                            <i data-lucide="share-2" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0f172a] group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Social Neuro-Impact</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Contenido diseñado para detener el scroll.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Modules -->
    <section class="py-32 px-8 lg:px-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-40">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600">Módulo 01 // SEO</div>
                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">VISIBILIDAD <br /> ESTRATÉGICA.</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Analizamos los algoritmos de búsqueda local para que tu negocio sea la primera respuesta. No es solo estar arriba, es ser la opción que genera confianza instantánea.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/strategy1/800/600" alt="Strategy" class="rounded-xl luxury-shadow">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Audit Section -->
    <section id="audit-section" class="py-40 px-8 relative">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-12">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
                    ¿ESTÁS LISTO PARA <br />
                    <span class="text-blue-600 italic font-serif">EL ANÁLISIS 360°?</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium">
                    No es una llamada de ventas. Es una auditoría estratégica. Si tu negocio tiene fugas de conversión, las encontraremos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-16 luxury-shadow relative text-left">
                <form class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 ml-1">Nombre Completo</label>
                            <input type="text" required placeholder="Ej. Juan Pérez" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 px-4 py-4 text-slate-900 font-sans text-sm focus:border-slate-900 focus:bg-white outline-none transition-all">
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 ml-1">Negocio Local</label>
                            <input type="text" required placeholder="Ej. Clínica Dental Avanzada" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 px-4 py-4 text-slate-900 font-sans text-sm focus:border-slate-900 focus:bg-white outline-none transition-all">
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 ml-1">Email Corporativo</label>
                            <input type="email" required placeholder="ejemplo@empresa.com" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 px-4 py-4 text-slate-900 font-sans text-sm focus:border-slate-900 focus:bg-white outline-none transition-all">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-2">
                        <input type="checkbox" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-slate-900 focus:ring-slate-900">
                        <label class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 leading-tight">
                            Acepto la política de privacidad para el tratamiento de mis datos.
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full mt-4 py-5 bg-[#1e293b] text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs transition-all shadow-xl hover:bg-[#0f172a] hover:-translate-y-1">
                        Solicitar Auditoría 360°
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="py-20 px-8 border-t border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-12">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#0f172a] flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">
                    <i data-lucide="layers" class="w-3 h-3 text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold tracking-tighter">JUANJE.</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
                &copy; 2026 // Ingeniería de Conversión
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Initialize Lucide icons
        lucide.createIcons();
        
        // Simple form handling
        document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            alert('¡Solicitud recibida! (Esto es un ejemplo, conecta tu formulario a un servicio real)');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
